A–C: male, holotype: A, habitus, upperside; B, habitus, underside; C, left forewing, upperside; D–F: female, paratype: D, habitus, upperside; E, habitus, underside; F, left forewing, upperside; G–H, female, paratype: wing venations: G, right forewing; H, right hind wing.
